body:
Serendipity

Pairing:Jimin x reader

Word count:379

•First of all ,the Vilvie planet is consisted  of only males.

•A female version exists but we will be focusing  on  the  male one,

Vilvia.

•So technically, Earth  is going  to spiral  to it's  own  destruction in a few hundred  years,so the high council  of the universe decided to save it.

•By sending  all females and males one by one in a secretive manner to another  planet.

•But did they really  have to do it like that?

•You'd  think the council  is just a bunch of people  who  want to see ships become cannon.

•So there it is, a very surprised  baby Jimin finding  about this whole  thing.

•Cause like, you mean to tell me that  I will receive a female that is my soul mate on my 20th birthday?

•Am I in a kdrama or something? On the other  hand baby Y/n knows absolutely  nothing.

•How jolly.

•So there it comes his 20th birthday.

•Jimin is beyond  excited.

•But first, let's  look at our handsome  fella other there.

•Jimin is part of the royal family,

 so he is unbelievably  handsome.

•He has raven black  hair and piercing  electric  blue eyes.

•His ears are pierced in several  places and adorned  with  exquisite  jewellery.

•His full lips are always  shining  with the natural lip gloss like shine that  Vilvie males possess.

•Even so, he likes wearing lipstick  just so his lips would  look extra good.

•His cheeks, elbows, tip of the nose, (and other special  places) have naturally  embeded glitter  in their skin.

•The catch is, that the glitter  shines with different  colours, representing  their  emotions.

•Other than his awesome  body,

he has one more  alien feature.

•Two little electric blue lines on his lower back, that hold some special apendages.

•(We will not talk about  that right now.)

 •For his clothing  choice, he usually  alters between bad boy and baby kitty.

•There  is no in between.

• As for his personality, we'll  describe him as a cutie pie with a little  perverted  edge.

(that will come in handy  later.)

•Between  his 6 brothers, he's  the shortest so he is teased a lot.

•Imagine an angry  baby chick, that is his face.

•But soon the angry  baby chick will meet his chicken, (I'm  sorry) so look  forward to that.

Word count:379

•First of all ,the Vilvie planet is consisted  of only males.

•A female version exists but we will be focusing  on  the  male one,

Vilvia.

•So technically, Earth  is going  to spiral  to it's  own  destruction in a few hundred  years,so the high council  of the universe decided to save it.

•By sending  all females and males one by one in a secretive manner to another  planet.

•But did they really  have to do it like that?

•You'd  think the council  is just a bunch of people  who  want to see ships become cannon.

•So there it is, a very surprised  baby Jimin finding  about this whole  thing.

•Cause like, you mean to tell me that  I will receive a female that is my soul mate on my 20th birthday?

•Am I in a kdrama or something? On the other  hand baby Y/n knows absolutely  nothing.

•How jolly.

•So there it comes his 20th birthday.

•Jimin is beyond  excited.

•But first, let's  look at our handsome  fella other there.

•Jimin is part of the royal family,

 so he is unbelievably  handsome.

•He has raven black  hair and piercing  electric  blue eyes.

•His ears are pierced in several  places and adorned  with  exquisite  jewellery.

•His full lips are always  shining  with the natural lip gloss like shine that  Vilvie males possess.

•Even so, he likes wearing lipstick  just so his lips would  look extra good.

•His cheeks, elbows, tip of the nose, (and other special  places) have naturally  embeded glitter  in their skin.

•The catch is, that the glitter  shines with different  colours, representing  their  emotions.

•Other than his awesome  body,

he has one more  alien feature.

•Two little electric blue lines on his lower back, that hold some special apendages.

•(We will not talk about  that right now.)

 •For his clothing  choice, he usually  alters between bad boy and baby kitty.

•There  is no in between.

• As for his personality, we'll  describe him as a cutie pie with a little  perverted  edge.

(that will come in handy  later.)

•Between  his 6 brothers, he's  the shortest so he is teased a lot.

•Imagine an angry  baby chick, that is his face.

•But soon the angry  baby chick will meet his chicken, (I'm  sorry) so look  forward to that.

by Velvetmica

“Load your gun, Koya. ” The guy with the alpaca mask whispered to the one with the koala one. Voice rough on the edges, giving simple yet threatening commands.

“Hell I still despise the idea of us in these masks with those codenames” The one with a mask looking like a cookie grumbled under his nose.

“Fucking shut up, Yoon-”

A loud thud echoed and the one with a yellow dog mask couldn’t finish his sentence.

The hallway went silent again. And the masked were sure it was way to quiet.

Click. Shoot.

“Fuck!” The scream pierced through everyone’s ears.

RJ walked out from behind the corner. “Tata.. I’m disappointed. He shouldn’t be able to scream if you hit the voal cords just the right way.” He sighs. “You still have a lot to learn.”

In a corrupt world where paid assassinations are the only way of dealing with problems the group of BT21 is the best at their job, never even once getting caught, never even once getting stopped.
